<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Withdrawal Notification</title>
    <style>
      .head-con {
        width: 100%;
        height: 40px;
        background-color: green;
        color: white;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      section {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="head-con">
        <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
      </div>
    </header>
    <section>
      <h2>Hello Thriftans, {{name}}</h2>
      <p>
        We have received your withdrawal request for the amount of {{amount}} naira. Your account will be credited within 1-2 business days.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you did not initiate this request, please update your account password immediately or contact us at <a href="mailto:support@Thriftify.com">support@Thriftify.com</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Should any additional information be required to process your withdrawal, we will reach out to you promptly.
      </p>
      <p>
        Kind regards,<br />
        The Thriftify Team
      </p>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
